{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/mysilkway/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"MySilkWay","caption":"","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/421a8/mysilkway-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/5efbf/mysilkway-logo.png 113w,\n/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/e9748/mysilkway-logo.png 225w,\n/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/421a8/mysilkway-logo.png 450w","sizes":"(min-width: 450px) 450px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/28652/mysilkway-logo.webp 113w,\n/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/b921d/mysilkway-logo.webp 225w,\n/static/9ed1e1c349c8f1c51e563613f3995407/cd8c7/mysilkway-logo.webp 450w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 450px) 450px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400.40000000000003}}}},"body":"<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\">\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mysilkway.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>See Live</u></a></p>\n<p>This Q&#x26;A box appears on all SKU pages. Logged in customers may ask a question about the product. Customers can also view published questions and rate them.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.18181818181819%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/c9b55/qna-demo-1.webp 165w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/f2908/qna-demo-1.webp 330w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/cc661/qna-demo-1.webp 660w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/a66df/qna-demo-1.webp 990w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/d33d4/qna-demo-1.webp 1320w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/38c53/qna-demo-1.webp 2862w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/04c57/qna-demo-1.png 165w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/d9ecf/qna-demo-1.png 330w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/1f083/qna-demo-1.png 660w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/7a3d6/qna-demo-1.png 990w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/78958/qna-demo-1.png 1320w,\n/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/bc81a/qna-demo-1.png 2862w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ac30d7f126c0bd3010125d4e6c3f876f/1f083/qna-demo-1.png\"\n            alt=\"MySilkWay - E-Commerce Platform\"\n            title=\"MySilkWay - E-Commerce Platform\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The admin portal handles received Q&#x26;As for all SKUs. It supports functions such as publish, unpublish, reply and ignore questions.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.181818181818183%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/c9b55/qna-demo-2.webp 165w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/f2908/qna-demo-2.webp 330w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/cc661/qna-demo-2.webp 660w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/a66df/qna-demo-2.webp 990w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/d33d4/qna-demo-2.webp 1320w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/4471c/qna-demo-2.webp 4575w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/04c57/qna-demo-2.png 165w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/d9ecf/qna-demo-2.png 330w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/1f083/qna-demo-2.png 660w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/7a3d6/qna-demo-2.png 990w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/78958/qna-demo-2.png 1320w,\n/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/41f48/qna-demo-2.png 4575w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3691803dcea54bc11a15d09c98ddb043/1f083/qna-demo-2.png\"\n            alt=\"MySilkWay - E-Commerce Platform\"\n            title=\"MySilkWay - E-Commerce Platform\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Front End using HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, while Back End using GoLang. We also used PostgresSQL for database and Docker for deploying the website.</p>\n</div>","categories":["Software Dev.","Internship"],"date":"September 01, 2019","description":"MySilkWay is an E-Commerce platform. This project is a Q&A portal for product pages. I've designed a frontend for customers to leave questions on a product, and an admin portal to maintain the questions.","id":"f7380710-4746-55a0-9cb2-84a9f800e61b","keywords":["Golang","Postgres","E-Commerce","Full-Stack"],"slug":"/mysilkway/","title":"Internship - MySilkWay","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1094019748","4239582004"],"slicesMap":{}}